        <abstract>
            <p>Philosophical Club dinner.</p>
            <p>Lyell contradicts W. B. Carpenter on current in Straits of Gibraltar.</p>
            <p>James Orton’s report on fossil shells found by L. Agassiz 2000 miles up the Amazon. Their identification disposes of the glacial hypothesis.</p>
            <p>No news yet from Gladstone on Ayrton affair.</p>
        </abstract>
